' Benign base package for the PKG-02b security fixture. `generate.py` builds
' this, then rewrites the compiled `.mfp` body into the malicious variant (a
' `run` whose IR does a member access on a *computed* Integer — a `Binary`
' result — exercising plan-20-C's completed member-confusion detection). The
' structured signature tables stay valid so the consumer still resolves
' `run() AS Integer`.
EXPORT FUNC run() AS Integer
  RETURN 42
END FUNC
